author: julianfoad
msg: Extract the code for resolving from (path or URL, symbolic revision) to
(operative URL, numeric revision) out of svn_client__ra_session_from_path()
into a separate function, to make the logic easier to follow, and also with
the anticipation of using this function in the near future.
